MBR.APPL_CU_NBR
,MBR.APPL_MB_NBR
,MBR.MB_FRST_NM1 as FRST_NM1
,MBR.MB_LAST_NM as LAST_NM
,CASE WHEN ADDR.APPL_ADDR_LINE_1_TXT IN (#ExclusionCode#) THEN ' ' ELSE ADDR.APPL_ADDR_LINE_1_TXT END as ADDR_LINE_1_TXT
,CASE WHEN ADDR.APPL_ADDR_LINE_2_TXT IN (#ExclusionCode#) THEN ' ' ELSE ADDR.APPL_ADDR_LINE_2_TXT END as ADDR_LINE_2_TXT
,CASE WHEN ADDR.APPL_CITY_NM IN (#ExclusionCode#) THEN ' ' ELSE ADDR.APPL_CITY_NM END as CITY_NM
,CASE WHEN ADDR.APPL_US_STATE_CD IN (#ExclusionCode#) THEN ' ' ELSE ADDR.APPL_US_STATE_CD END as US_STATE_CD
,CASE WHEN ADDR.APPL_POSTL_CD IN (#ExclusionCode#) THEN ' ' ELSE ADDR.APPL_POSTL_CD END as POSTL_CD
,CAST(CAST(MBR.BIRTH_DT AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS VARCHAR(10)) BIRTH_DT1
,CASE WHEN MBR.GNDR_TYP_CD IN (#ExclusionCode#) THEN ' ' ELSE MBR.GNDR_TYP_CD END as GNDR_TYP_CD1
,SPAN.APPL_TRGT_ADJUD_SYS_CD
,CASE WHEN MBR.DEPNDT_TYP_DSC IN (#ExclusionCode#) THEN ' ' ELSE MBR.DEPNDT_TYP_DSC END as DEPNDT_TYP_DSC1
,MBR.APPL_CNSMR_OFFER_NBR
,CASE WHEN MBR.CNSMR_CNTRT_TYP_DSC IN (#ExclusionCode#) THEN ' ' ELSE MBR.CNSMR_CNTRT_TYP_DSC END as CNSMR_CNTRT_TYP_DSC1
,MBR.EFF_END_DT
,CASE WHEN MBR.EFF_END_DT > CAST ('#LastDt#' AS DATE) THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END AS ELIGIBILITY_STATUS
,CAST(CASE WHEN MBR.EFF_END_DT > CAST ('#LastDt#' AS DATE) THEN NULL ELSE CAST( MBR.EFF_END_DT AS CHAR(10) ) END AS DATE) AS UNENROLLMENT_DATE
,CAST(CAST(UNENROLLMENT_DATE AS DATE FORMAT 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS VARCHAR(10)) UNENROLLMENT_DATE1
,RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY MBR.APPL_CU_NBR,MBR.APPL_MB_NBR ORDER BY MBR.EFF_END_DT DESC) AS RNK QUALIFY RNK = 1
FROM
#TDDatabaseExtrcMth#.#SrcTable# MBR
INNER JOIN #TDDatabaseSmtcMth#.#SrcTable2# SPAN
ON SPAN.MB_CNTRT_JOIN_ID = MBR.MB_CNTRT_JOIN_ID
INNER JOIN #TDDatabaseWrkVw#.#SrcTable3# PY_PARM
ON MBR.APPL_CU_NBR = PY_PARM.EXTRC_PARM_VAL
OR MBR.APPL_GRP_NBR = PY_PARM.EXTRC_PARM_VAL
OR MBR.APPL_CNSMR_OFFER_NBR = PY_PARM.EXTRC_PARM_VAL
LEFT OUTER JOIN
(SELECT
APPL_MB_NBR,
EFF_BEG_DT,
EFF_END_DT,
APPL_ADDR_LINE_1_TXT,
APPL_ADDR_LINE_2_TXT,
APPL_CITY_NM,
APPL_US_STATE_CD,
APPL_POSTL_CD,
EDW_PY_MB_JOIN_KEY
QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY EDW_PY_MB_JOIN_KEY ORDER BY ADDR_RNK ASC, EFF_END_DT DESC) = 1
/* This will pick addresses in the order of preference as stated in #3
*/
FROM (
SELECT
APPL_MB_NBR,
EFF_BEG_DT,
EFF_END_DT,
APPL_ADDR_LINE_1_TXT,
APPL_ADDR_LINE_2_TXT,
APPL_CITY_NM,
APPL_US_STATE_CD,
APPL_POSTL_CD,
EDW_PY_MB_JOIN_KEY
, CASE WHEN DATE BETWEEN EFF_BEG_DT AND EFF_END_DT THEN 1
WHEN EFF_BEG_DT> DATE THEN 2
WHEN EFF_END_DT < DATE THEN 3
ELSE 4 END ADDR_RNK
FROM #TDDatabaseSmtcMth#.#SrcTable4#
WHERE LOC_USE_TYP_CD = '#LocUseTypCd#'
and EDW_PY_MB_JOIN_KEY<>0
)BST
)ADDR
ON MBR.PY_MB_JOIN_KEY = ADDR.EDW_PY_MB_JOIN_KEY
WHERE
MBR.EFF_END_DT >= ' #StartDt#'
AND PY_PARM.EXTRC_PARM_CAT_CD = '#ExtrcParmCatCd#'
ORDER BY MBR.APPL_CU_NBR,MBR.APPL_MB_NBR]]><Tables collapsed='1'></Tables><Parameters collapsed='1'></Parameters><Columns collapsed='1'></Columns></SelectStatement></SQL><Transaction><RecordCount modified='1' type='int'><![CDATA[1000]]></RecordCount><EndOfWave collapsed='1' type='int'><![CDATA[0]]></EndOfWave></Transaction><Session><IsolationLevel type='int'><![CDATA[1]]></IsolationLevel><ArraySize modified='1' type='int'><![CDATA[10]]></ArraySize><SchemaReconciliation><FailOnSizeMismatch type='bool'><![CDATA[1]]></FailOnSizeMismatch><FailOnTypeMismatch type='bool'><![CDATA[1]]></FailOnTypeMismatch></SchemaReconciliation><PassLobLocator collapsed='1' type='bool'><![CDATA[0]]></PassLobLocator></Session><BeforeAfter collapsed='1' type='bool'><![CDATA[0]]></BeforeAfter><BulkAccess><Sleep type='int'><![CDATA[0]]></Sleep><Tenacity type='int'><![CDATA[0]]></Tenacity></BulkAccess><LimitSettings><MaxSessions type='int'><![CDATA[0]]></MaxSessions><MaxPartitionSessions type='int'><![CDATA[0]]></MaxPartitionSessions><MinSessions type='int'><![CDATA[0]]></MinSessions><MaxBufferSize modified='1' type='int'><![CDATA[700000]]></MaxBufferSize><ProgressInterval modified='1' type='int'><![CDATA[0]]></ProgressInterval></LimitSettings><ParallelSynchronization collapsed='1' type='bool'><![CDATA[0]]></ParallelSynchronization><LimitRows collapsed='1' type='bool'><![CDATA[0]]></LimitRows></Usage></Properties >
